Substantial modifications and additions made by the kirocc-pro
project. See the commit history and files marked with `// [fork]`
for the full set of changes; the most prominent additions are:

  * 8 protocol-hardening fixes on top of the upstream Anthropic ↔ Kiro
    translator (see README_3460_OPTIMIZED.md).
  * A web admin UI (internal/admin/) with multi-account pool
    management, per-account proxies, region-aware routing, multi
    API key auth with expiry and token quotas, usage attribution
    by key and device, and remote API automation.
  * Per-credential outbound HTTP client cache for proxy isolation
    (internal/proxyhttp/).
  * GeoIP-driven region preference using MaxMind GeoLite2-Country
    (internal/georegion/).
  * Runtime-mutable settings store with optimization knob
    persistence (internal/settings/).

The upstream kirocc project is unaffiliated with this fork; please
direct fork-specific issues to the kirocc-pro repository, and
upstream protocol issues to d-kuro/kirocc.
